In the end, developers will decide which solutions gain market adoption.

Underestimating Ethereum or others because they have gas assets seems like a blind spot in your thinking.

@SDLerner @lightcoin @RSKsmart @Liquid_BTC @ethereum @Namecoin @Stacks I wouldnâ€™t qualify Stacks or Namecoin to be sidechains. (Ethereum is just a separate network with nothing to do with Bitcoin).

Namecoin was merged mined.

